 *
 * Built-in support for:
 * - Drupal Coding Standards - http://drupal.org/node/318
 * - Handle text in a secure fashion - http://drupal.org/node/28984
 * - Converting 4.6.x modules to 4.7.x - http://drupal.org/node/22218
